episodes.title: Logan’s Journey: From Cult to Combat to Live TV Director
episodes.description:
In this episode of Spirits & Stories with Donald Dunn, Logan shares his powerful journey.

He grew up in a strict religious cult in Chicago, battled poverty, and faced suicidal thoughts as a child. Seeking freedom, he joined the Air Force, serving 12 years with two tours in Iraq. After coming home, Logan struggled with depression, divorce, and rebuilding his life.

Today, he’s a successful live TV director, having worked on the World Series, French Open, and Super Bowl. Logan’s story is about resilience, transformation, and never giving up on your dreams.

👉 Follow Logan: https://theloganunlimited.com
